name: Full Body Ape #12
description: From the creators of the infamous Bored Ape Yacht Club, the most ambitious NFT project has been released: the Full Body Apes. This is an all new NFT collection of fully illustrated Bored Ape artworks like you have never seen them before. Full Body Apes has been promised to be the next big hit that would shake up the NFT market in the future days. Only more than a thousand of this rare collection will be minted so don't hesitate to grab yourself one for huge profits in return, but also to gain access to future rewards that will soon be revealed.
